Recommendation for Free vs Paid Model:
Free Tier:

Custom rule support (basic resources like Pods, Deployments, etc.)

Basic error handling and rule validation

Small-scale scanning with some filtering options

Basic report generation (text-based)

Limited support (community-driven support or forum access)

Paid Tier:

Advanced custom rule support (regex, logical conditions)

Full resource support (Pods, Services, ConfigMaps, Secrets, etc.)

Asynchronous scanning with parallel execution

Advanced reporting (PDF, HTML with detailed remediation)

Full-scale scanning (unlimited resources)

Integration with CI/CD pipelines and API

Premium support (24/7 with SLA)

Advanced RBAC and audit log management
